In the coming months, my office will be conducting interviews with veterans interested in preserving their stories and history at the Library of Congress. To learn more and to sign up to participate, click here: https://bit.ly/2YvK1wK
The Veterans History Project collects first-hand accounts of veterans through audio and video recordings and with collections of original photographs, letters, and diaries.

ICYMI: I recently announced the Veterans History Project – a partnership between my office and @librarycongress to permanently preserve the oral histories of Alaska’s veterans. pic.twitter.com/bEd84WvV4z
